<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Signup</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background: #f1f1f1;
    }
    .signup-container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background: #fff;
      display: flex;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .left-panel {
      flex: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0072ff, #00c6ff);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 50px 30px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .left-panel h2 {
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .right-panel {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .form-control, textarea {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      resize: none;
    }
    .btn-main {
      width: 100%;
      height: 50px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #0072ff;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
    }
    .btn-main:hover {
      background: #005fd4;
    }
    .social-icons i {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin: 0 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: #0072ff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="signup-container">
    
   
    <div class="left-panel">
      <h2>Come join us!</h2>
      <p>We are so excited to have you here. If you havenâ€™t already, create an account to get access to exclusive offers, rewards, and discounts.</p>
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-light mt-3 px-4 py-2 rounded-pill">Already have an account? Signin</a>
    </div>

    
    <div class="right-panel">
      <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">Signup</h2>
      <form method="post" action="" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Username" name="username" required>
        <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Email" name="email" required>
        <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Password" name="password" required>
        
       
        <textarea name="bio" rows="3" class="form-control" placeholder="Write your bio..."></textarea>
        
      
        <label for="avatar" class="form-label">Upload Avatar</label>
        <input type="file" class="form-control" name="avatar" id="avatar">
        
        <button type="submit" class="btn-main mt-3">Signup</button>
      </form>

      <p class="text-center mt-3">or signup with</p>
      <div class="text-center social-icons">
        <i class="bi bi-facebook"></i>
        <i class="bi bi-google"></i>
        <i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
